{"pageProps":{"note":{"id":"OCBJDED8DhgRzfr9tuqIE","title":"FRED","vault":{"fsPath":"vault"},"type":"note","desc":"","links":[],"anchors":{"fredmd":{"type":"header","text":"FREDMD","value":"fredmd","line":10,"column":0},"fredqd":{"type":"header","text":"FREDQD","value":"fredqd","line":45,"column":0}},"fname":"Datasets.FRED","updated":1636077341065,"created":1635402071090,"parent":"jtZSk246bVVDfJy6cdpS1","children":[],"data":{},"contentHash":"cc9fe88f6ddc52cf2f5b9b2c12fb9a12","custom":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"fred\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading\" href=\"#fred\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a>FRED</h1>\n<p>Documentation regarding the FRED Data. Split into FREDMD and FREDQD sections.</p>\n<h2 id=\"fredmd\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading\" href=\"#fredmd\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a>FREDMD</h2>\n<p>Data cleaning issues:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>ANDENOx = New Orders for Nondefense Capital Goods, starts from 1968 03</li>\n<li>TWEXMMTH = Trade Weighted US DOllar Index , starts from 1973-02</li>\n<li>UMCSNETx = Consumer Sentiment Index, starts from 1978 02</li>\n<li>ACOGNO = New orders for Consumer Goods, starts from 1992 02</li>\n<li>VXOCLSx = VXO index, starts from 1962-07</li>\n</ul>\n<p>ISM series were discontinued after 2016 after a falling out between FRED and ISM. These were kept in the dataset for legacy reasons, but present a missing data problem.\nThe ISM series are:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>ID 19 NAPMPI</li>\n<li>ID 49 NAPMEI</li>\n<li>ID 60 NAPM</li>\n<li>ID 61 NAPMNOI</li>\n<li>ID 62 NAPMSDI</li>\n<li>ID 63 MAPMII</li>\n<li>ID 112 NAPMPRI</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Some important series (perhaps keep in mind for thresholding)</p>\n<p>Inflation related variables</p>\n<ul>\n<li>WPSFD49207 = PPI of finished goods</li>\n<li>CPIAUCSL = CPI of all items</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Recession related variables</p>\n<ul>\n<li>RPI = real personal income</li>\n<li>INDPRO = Industrial Production</li>\n<li>UNRATE = unemployment rate</li>\n<li>UEMPMEAN = mean duration of unemployment</li>\n<li>HOUST = Housing Starts</li>\n<li>FEDFUNDS = effective federal funds rate</li>\n<li>S.P.500 = SP500 index</li>\n<li>VXOCLSx = VXO index</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"fredqd\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading\" href=\"#fredqd\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a>FREDQD</h2>\n<p>Quarterly version of FRED data, much higher N dimension, much lower T dimension</p>\n<p>Missing Data Issues:</p>\n<p>Important Series (possible future thresholding):</p>\n<ul>\n<li></li>\n</ul>","noteIndex":{"id":"PhD","title":"PhD Homepage","vault":{"fsPath":"vault"},"type":"note","desc":"","links":[{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"PhD","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"roadmap","alias":"roadmap","position":{"start":{"line":12,"column":1,"offset":451},"end":{"line":12,"column":12,"offset":462},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"roadmap"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"PhD","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"Meeting","alias":"Meeting","position":{"start":{"line":14,"column":1,"offset":464},"end":{"line":14,"column":12,"offset":475},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"Meeting"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"PhD","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"TODO","alias":"TODO","position":{"start":{"line":16,"column":1,"offset":477},"end":{"line":16,"column":9,"offset":485},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"TODO"}}],"anchors":{"quick-links":{"type":"header","text":"Quick Links","value":"quick-links","line":17,"column":0}},"fname":"root","updated":1637563604861,"created":1595961348801,"parent":null,"children":["t58wEmhAtf1GlHmO","Wnsnl9Ff8hLGapBoL37BK","CQTUwoXQNcd0Y7la7IaAn","9s2d4L1UHWFWCdtORYT2Q","AiXOWFsdvi3BPZxcUMjIi","MsmFdXyWfizd5g8GGcObD","MXHvc8bQbNRRVCB0UogRy","T4FN6sDHfA9wxiZ7Dg5WX","jtZSk246bVVDfJy